---
title: Black Pepper Tofu & Snow Pea Stir-Fry with Garlic Rice
description: You're going to get a kick out of this one. We've got a colourful team of snow peas, carrot and red onion bound together in a kecap manis coating peppered with... you guessed it, black pepper! You'll give the peppercorns a pummel to release their flavour, then stir them into the tofu-veggie mix to make a stir-fry that'll knock your socks off.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/black-pepper-tofu-snow-pea-stir-fry-ee399d61.jpg
